a second-hand murder, Larry.

1031
01:26:10,320 --> 01:26:12,441
It's been a second-hand
marriage too.

1032
01:27:59,920 --> 01:28:01,480
It's a full confession.

1033
01:28:03,200 --> 01:28:05,160
You can play it to the police
when they come.

1034
01:28:07,320 --> 01:28:08,280
It's up to you.

1035
01:28:10,800 --> 01:28:11,960
I'm guilty.

1036
01:28:13,960 --> 01:28:16,000
You're guilty of being a fool.
